Hello!<br />I'm currently trying to develop a compatibility layer to compile GBDK games to devkitSMS. <br /><br /><a href="https://github.com/haroldo-ok/sms-gbdk-compat" class="postlink">https://github.com/haroldo-ok/sms-gbdk-compat</a><br /><br />This is a work in progress. So far, only the 'galaxy' and 'dscan' examples have been tested; they still needed some minor changes to the source, but the compatibility layer did save a lot of time.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=4777">haroldo-ok</a> — Fri Sep 25, 2015 4:47 pm</p><hr />
